 Once upon  atime in a forest, there lived a monkey who resides on a jamon tree, which was on the banks of river. and in the same forest
there lived a crocodile and his wife.................. one day , the crocodile came to the banks of the river and
rested under tree.The kindhearted monkey offered him some fruits. The crocodilecame back the next day for more fruits, as he loved tgem.
As days passed the crocodile and the monkey became good friends.
